display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>. Suppose that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> satisfies the
<fr:em>solution set condition</fr:em>: for each object <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[c]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex>, there exists a
<fr:link
