display="inline"><![CDATA[c\xrightarrow {f_i} Gd_i]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> such that any map
<fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[c\xrightarrow {f} Gd]]></fr:tex> factors through one of the <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f_i]]></fr:tex> via the <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex>-image of a map
<fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[d_i\to  d]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex> admits a <fr:link
